{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/Mijn-eerste-game-in-pygame/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>Het tweede project wat ik voor mijn opleiding heb gemaakt was een game, gemaakt met Pygame. Pygame is een opensource game engine gemaakt in Python.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/362918fd5b64a4fef64847e5d050e17a/7e26b/pygame1.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 59.50920245398773%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"pygame euromast the game\"\n        title=\"pygame euromast the game\"\n        src=\"/static/362918fd5b64a4fef64847e5d050e17a/6aca1/pygame1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/362918fd5b64a4fef64847e5d050e17a/d2f63/pygame1.jpg 163w,\n/static/362918fd5b64a4fef64847e5d050e17a/c989d/pygame1.jpg 325w,\n/static/362918fd5b64a4fef64847e5d050e17a/6aca1/pygame1.jpg 650w,\n/static/362918fd5b64a4fef64847e5d050e17a/7c09c/pygame1.jpg 975w,\n/static/362918fd5b64a4fef64847e5d050e17a/01ab0/pygame1.jpg 1300w,\n/static/362918fd5b64a4fef64847e5d050e17a/7e26b/pygame1.jpg 1510w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/Steven24K/Project-2-Game\">Bron code</a></p>\n<p>De game was origineel gebouwd voor Python 3.6, later heb ik een versie gemaakt die compatable is met Python 3.6. De dependency met de PostgreSQL database is komen te vervallen.</p>\n<h1>Euromast The Game</h1>\n<p>Doel spel: Zoveel mogelijk vragen over Rotterdam correct beantwoorden en als eerste de top van de Euromast bereiken. </p>\n<iframe width=\"900\" height=\"506\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/NOCupqNu5Ts\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe>","frontmatter":{"title":"Mijn eerste game met Pygame","date":"2017-01-28","category":"Projects"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/Mijn-eerste-game-in-pygame/"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3309693220","3318396998","3649515864","63159454"]}